00:38:10,560 --> 00:38:11,560
Lumabas para makipag-chat.

497
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:13,880
Halika na.

498
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:22,520
Ito...

499
00:38:22,600 --> 00:38:23,600
(Molten Lava)

500
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,360
parang ang recipe ko.

501
00:38:28,160 --> 00:38:29,160
Huwag mag-alala tungkol sa recipe.

502
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:30,160
Bibigyan kita ng bago.

503
00:38:30,520 --> 00:38:31,520
Seryoso ito.

504
00:38:39,120 --> 00:38:40,240
I've tried my best.

505
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,680
Hindi ko talaga masabi kung ano ito.

506
00:38:42,680 --> 00:38:43,680
sa tingin ko...

507
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:44,800
minsan,

508
00:38:45,040 --> 00:38:46,040
mataas ang IQ...

509
00:38:46,640 --> 00:38:48,440
hindi maaaring maging kasing ganda
ng tunay na pagkilala sa tao.

510
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:50,800
Jiang Xiao Shuai.

511
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:53,840
Lima, walo, walo, walo.

512
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:56,000
Lima, walo, walo,

513
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:57,840
walo.

514
00:38:59,920 --> 00:39:00,920
walo...

515
00:39:02,640 --> 00:39:03,760
mayaman ako.

516
00:39:05,240 --> 00:39:07,120
Binigyan ba siya ng iyong ama
ng maraming pera?

517
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:09,640
Ang five-twenty ay madaling maunawaan.

518
00:39:10,480 --> 00:39:11,520
Ito ay "Mahal kita."

519
00:39:11,680 --> 00:39:12,680
