520
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:19,600
- Sige na.
- Naiintindihan ko na.

521
00:39:20,880 --> 00:39:22,560
"I love you. Bye."

522
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:25,440
Kaya kung ikinonekta mo sila,

523
00:39:25,640 --> 00:39:27,320
Binigyan siya ng iyong ama ng maraming pera...

524
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,440
at tinatrato siya ng maayos.

525
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:29,480
Hindi mo kailangang mag-alala.

526
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:30,960
Bye.

527
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,280
Kahanga-hanga.

528
00:39:38,360 --> 00:39:39,600
Mabuti pang umuwi na ako bukas.
